Doc: The method by which the Flat Rate is calculated for a commodity freight transaction.

Source.Contents:
/#
 The method by which the Flat Rate is calculated for a commodity freight transaction.
 #/
enum FpML5.transparency.FlatRateEnum {
    # The Flat Rate will be the New Worldwide Tanker Nominal Freight Scale for the Freight Index Route for the Trade Date for the transaction.
    Fixed 
    # The Flat Rate for each Pricing Date will be the New Worldwide Tanker Nominal Freight Scale for the Freight Index Route for the Pricing Date..
    Floating 

}

Fixed.Doc: The Flat Rate will be the New Worldwide Tanker Nominal Freight Scale for the Freight Index Route for the Trade Date for the transaction.
Fixed.Name: Fixed

Floating.Doc: The Flat Rate for each Pricing Date will be the New Worldwide Tanker Nominal Freight Scale for the Freight Index Route for the Pricing Date..
Floating.Name: Floating
